org.softlang.megal

Interface MegalRelationshipType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, MegalDeclaration, MegalElement, MegalNamed, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MegalRelationshipTypeImpl

    public interface MegalRelationshipType
extends MegalNamed
    A representation of the model object 'Relationship Type'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Left
    • Right
    • Left Both
    • Right Both
    • Left Many
    • Right Many
    • Left Params
    • Right Params
    See Also:
    MegalPackage.getMegalRelationshipType()
